des: Try these checklists to help scheduled cleaning services on what to focus on when cleaning your house. This checklist makes sure these services are cleaning the parts and items of the house. Further, it allows the services to provide a list of cleaning supplies needed the next time they service the house. you stay organized. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint.
